    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は雑誌のグラビア撮影に来た）\n（サニピのみんなではなく、雫単独での撮影だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Today a photographer came for a gravure shoot‚)\n(not for all of Sunny Peace‚ but just for Shizuku.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "むむっ……\nあんなに沢山、スタッフさん達が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*mumble*\nThere are so many staff there…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "それに……あの衣装……\n私に着こなせる、かな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And that outfit…\nCan I wear it well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、不安か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you nervous after all?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、頑張る\n頑張らないと、ダメ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… I’ll do my best.\nI have to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "あの子と約束したんだから\n私もちゃんとアイドルしないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I promised that girl‚\nso if I don’t act like a proper idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あの子？\nあのファンレターの子か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“That girl”?\nThe one who wrote that fan letter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "そう、私の大切なファン……絶対に裏切れない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ my precious fan. I’ll never betray her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……\nよし、じゃあ、行こうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nAlright then‚ shall we go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.2
    },
    {
