      "text": "表情……硬い、ですか？　もっと笑顔……\nはい、出来ます……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is my expression too stiff? Smile more?\nYes‚ I can do that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
