      "text": "（あなたは私にそっくりです）\n（だからアイドルになる夢を、諦めないで下さい……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(You’re just like me.)\n(That’s why you should never give up on your dream of becoming an idol.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
